node.title: Wonderland
node.description: One of our favorite falls to see on our trip to the Smokies was this unnamed falls right off the road near Cherokee.  This portion cannot be seen from the road, but is no more than .1 mile from a small pull-off.  This was a great spot to explore and avoid the crowds.
